    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020130/extras/d3c2195db46d2c15a14cd4c98c59843a.webp?t=1765511244\" width=393 height=46 /></span><br><strong>FOXLORE</strong> follows the adventure of <strong>Filo</strong>, a cunning fox who stumbles upon a mysterious map leading to an ancient relic of untold power. As Filo unravels the secrets of the relic, he uncovers hidden truths that could change the fate of his world forever.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020130/extras/3cd071c1c2c08f92ee414b4023110893.webp?t=1765511244\" width=421 height=46 /></span><br>Navigate through a world in decay, meet new friends and familiar faces, and discover hidden clues to the mysteries at hand. Explore the rust belt, uncover the gothic fall from glory of the old world, learn the history of the new one, and unravel the rich story that binds the fate of <strong>Filo</strong> to the powerful relic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020130/extras/8d48778f88b7e4025951408a14b87bcf.webp?t=1765511244\" width=564 height=46 /></span><br>As the secrets of the old world unravel, <strong>Filo</strong> encounters story-driven puzzles that stand in his way. Each puzzle is a key to unlocking the murky truth behind the ancient relic, challenging Filo at every turn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020130/extras/a2a969ad8c416955293ff82b6727f044.avif?t=1765511244\" width=564 height=157 /></span>",
